% Course Information
\section*{Course Information}
\textbf{Instructor:} David Earn\\
\textbf{Course Dates:} 2025-01-06 -- 2025-04-08\\
\textbf{Units:} 3.00\\
\textbf{Course Delivery Mode:} Research\\
\textbf{Course Description:} Directed reading in areas of mathematics of interest to the student and the instructor. This course includes a scientific communication component. Prerequisite(s): GPA of at least 7.0 and permission of the Chair of the Department. MATH 4W03 may be repeated if on a different topic.

